  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "Synthetic V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package intentionally omits hasApplicabilityConstraint and hasOperatingEnvelope on the ContextOfUse, leaving the model's valid range of use unspecified in structured form (W-ON-02). Prose description references operating conditions but no machine-readable envelope is bound.",
