      "acceptanceCriteria": "The hemolysis index QoI must be directly linked to the clinical endpoint (chronic hemolysis threshold) with documented traceability.",
      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is mapped to the Giersiepen power-law model and linked to the clinical NIH threshold. Traceability documentation exists but does not address species-specific sensitivity of the power-law exponents."
