      "acceptanceCriteria": "All uncertain model inputs (power-law coefficients, blood viscosity, inlet velocity profile) must be characterized with probability distributions and propagated via Monte Carlo UQ.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ was initiated; inlet velocity and viscosity distributions were defined. Power-law coefficients were treated as fixed nominal values rather than uncertain inputs, leaving a significant gap in input uncertainty characterization."
