    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team accepted the package for submission despite all seven assessed factors falling below required levels and six factors remaining unassessed. The decision was based on the completeness of prose documentation and the Monte Carlo UQ effort, which were deemed sufficient for a preliminary regulatory interaction. The absence of structured applicability constraints and operating envelope definitions was not flagged as a formal gap; operating ranges are described in prose within the COU description only.",
